据世卫组织新冠肺炎情况报告，截至欧洲中部时间7日10时(北京时间7日17时)，中国境外新冠肺炎确诊病例数达到21110例，死亡413例。
According to the WHO New Crown Pneumonia Report, the number of confirmed cases of pneumonia outside China reached 21,100, with 413 deaths, as of 1000 CET (7: 00 Beijing time).
其中，从3月7日零时至8日零时，意大利新冠肺炎确诊病例新增1332例，累计确诊病例已增至6012例。
From 0000 hours on March 7 to 0000 hours on March 8, 1,332 new cases were confirmed in Italy, bringing the total number of confirmed cases to 6,012.
为了应对全国持续恶化的新冠肺炎疫情，意大利总理孔特于7日晚10时紧急召开内阁部长联席会议，决定将意大利伦巴第大区所辖市镇，以及其他大区所辖的11座城市纳入新的红色隔离区。
In response to the worsening outbreak of pneumonia in the country, Italian Prime Minister Conte convened a joint meeting of cabinet ministers at 10: 00 pm on Tuesday night and decided to include the new red zone in the Italian city of Lombardy, as well as in 11 other regional municipalities.
中国境外确诊病例超2万世卫组织：各国需采取强力措施如今，全球新冠肺炎确诊病例超过10万例，世卫组织呼吁各国采取强力措施，抑制并逆转病毒蔓延。
Confirmed cases outside China exceed 20,000: Countries need to take strong measures Today, there are more than 100,000 confirmed cases of pneumonia worldwide, and WHO calls on countries to take strong measures to contain and reverse the spread of the virus.
截至3月1日16时，韩国新冠肺炎累计确诊病例达到3736个。
As of 16: 00 on March 1, the cumulative number of confirmed cases of New Crown Pneumonia in Korea reached 3,736.
世卫组织每日疫情报告显示，截至欧洲中部时间7日10时(北京时间17时)，中国以外新冠肺炎确诊病例较前一日增加3633例，达到21110例；死亡病例较前一日增加78例，达到413例。
According to the WHO Daily Epidemiology Report, confirmed cases of new crown pneumonia outside China had increased by 3,633 cases to 21,100 compared with the previous day, and the number of deaths had increased by 78 cases to 413 as compared with the previous day.
全球范围内，新冠肺炎确诊病例比前一日增加3735例，达到101927例。
Globally, the number of confirmed cases of new crown pneumonia increased by 3,735 from the previous day to 101,927.
Play视频资料：3月6日，韩国修法禁止疫情期间出口医疗物资世卫组织呼吁所有国家继续做出努力，以有效抑制病例数量并减缓病毒传播。
World Health Organization calls on all nations to continue their efforts to effectively curb the number of cases and slow the spread of the virus.
世卫组织7日发表声明称，中国和其他国家的行动表明，可以通过采取普遍适用的措施来减缓病毒的传播并减少影响，这些行动包括：通过全社会努力来查找和治疗病人，追踪接触者，使医院和诊所做好病人剧增时的处理准备，以及培训卫生工作者。
China and other countries have taken steps to slow the spread of the virus and reduce its impact through community-wide efforts to identify and treat patients, track contacts, prepare hospitals and clinics to deal with surges, and train health workers, the WHO said in a statement.
Play视频资料：中国已向巴基斯坦、日本、非盟等提供检测试剂同时，世卫组织还表示，将继续与所有国家、合作伙伴和专家网络合作，协调开展国际应对，制定指导方针，分发物资，分享知识，并向人们提供保护自己和他人所需的信息。
Play Video: While China has provided testing reagents to Pakistan, Japan, the African Union and others, WHO says it will continue to work with all countries, partners and expert networks to coordinate an international response, develop guidelines, distribute materials, share knowledge and provide people with the information they need to protect themselves and others.
意大利单日新增确诊病例1332例伦巴第大区全面封城据欧联网援引欧联通讯社报道，意大利紧急民防部、新冠肺炎疫情新闻中心8日凌晨通报，从3月7日零时至8日零时，意大利新冠肺炎确诊病例新增1332例，累计确诊病例已增至6012例，一次核酸检测呈阳性反应疑似病例升至5190例，其中重症患者567人，累计死亡患者达到233人。
Italy confirmed 1,332 new cases in one day The European Union news agency reported on the Internet that between 0000 and 0000 hours March 7, Italy's new crown pneumonia confirmed 1332 cases, cumulative confirmed cases have increased to 6,012, a positive nucleic acid test suspected cases rose to 5,190, 567 of them serious cases, the cumulative number of deaths reached 233.
Play视频资料：意大利总统马塔雷拉3月5日发表电视讲话，号召民众遵循政府做出的防疫部署，团结一致应对疫情，并强调对意大利早日战胜疫情充满信心。
Italian President Matarela on Monday called on people to follow the government's anti-epidemic plan and unite in the fight against the epidemic, stressing his country's confidence in an early end to the epidemic.
据报道，当地时间8日凌晨，意大利紧急民防部部长、新冠肺炎疫情新闻发言人安吉洛•博雷利(Angelo Borrelli)表示，意大利疫情目前已从7日的89座城市，蔓延至93座城市，全国治愈患者共计589例。
According to reports, early Monday morning local time, Angelo Borrelli, Italy's minister of emergency civil defence and spokesman for the New Crown Pneumonia epidemic, said the outbreak had spread from 89 cities on the 7th to 93 cities, with 589 cases cured nationwide.
博雷利表示，为了应对全国持续恶化的新冠肺炎疫情，总理孔特于7日晚10时紧急召开内阁部长联席会议，研议应对疫情的政策和措施。
In response to the worsening outbreak of pneumonia in the country, Prime Minister Conte called an emergency meeting of cabinet ministers at 10 p.m. on Thursday to discuss policies and measures to tackle the epidemic, he said.
经内阁部长会议研究决定，意大利伦巴第大区所辖市镇，以及其他大区所辖的11座城市将纳入新的红色隔离区。
By decision of the Council of Ministers, the municipalities of the region of Lombardy, Italy, as well as the 11 municipalities of other regions, will be added to the new red zone.
除执行任务的军警、医护人员和紧急救援人员，红色隔离区禁止所有人员出入。
The Red Zone of Separation is closed to all personnel except uniformed personnel, medical personnel and emergency personnel on mission.
博雷利强调，被最新纳入红色隔离区的除伦巴第大区所辖的米兰市等所有市镇外，其他被隔离的包括摩德纳、帕尔马、皮亚琴察、雷焦艾米利亚、里米尼、佩萨罗-乌尔比诺、威尼斯、帕多瓦、特雷维索、阿斯提和亚里桑德里亚。
Borrelli stressed that, with the exception of all municipalities recently included in the Red Zone of Separation, including Milan, which is under the jurisdiction of the Lombardy region, the rest are Modena, Parma, Piacenza, Reggio Emilia, Rimini, Pesaro-Urbino, Venice, Padua, Treviso, Asti and Alexandria.
博雷利表示，新的地区和城市隔离法令从8日零时开始实施，隔离时间暂定为4月3日结束，具体隔离时间将视疫情发展情况而定。
Borelli said the new regional and city isolation order will be implemented from 0 pm on the 8th, the temporary isolation period is set to end on April 3, depending on the development of the epidemic.
目前负责执行隔离任务的军警人员已开赴隔离区戒备。
Military and police personnel currently assigned to the area of separation are on alert.
博雷利指出，根据总理孔特签署的最新法令，被纳入红色隔离区的大区和城市的体育馆、游泳馆，健康中心、博物馆、文化中心等公众设施全部关闭。
According to Borrelli, according to the latest decree signed by Prime Minister Conte, all public facilities, including sports halls, swimming pools, health centres, museums and cultural centres, have been integrated into the Red Zone of Separation regions and cities.
所有幼儿园、中小学校和大学全部停课。
All kindergartens, schools and universities are closed.
法令规定，购物场所除周末外不得关闭，必须保证民众日常生活用品和食物的供应；红色隔离区的所有民间婚丧仪式、宗教活动等全部暂停，禁止举办任何文化、娱乐、体育和集会等各种社会活动，电影院、剧院、夜总会、游戏厅和博彩投注服务机构等全部暂停。
The decree stipulates that shopping places may not be closed except on weekends, that the supply of daily necessities and food to the population must be guaranteed; that all civil ceremonies and religious activities in the red zone of separation are suspended; that all social activities, such as culture, entertainment, sports and gatherings; and that cinemas, theatres, nightclubs, game halls and betting services are suspended.
法令同时规定，境内所有民众、移民和外国游客若发现呼吸道症状，以及体温达到37.5度，应立即拨打应急救助电话，并留在住所等待医护人员前来诊治，严禁外出与社会接触。
The decree also stipulates that all citizens, immigrants and foreign tourists who discover respiratory symptoms and have a body temperature of 37.5 degrees should call the emergency number immediately and stay at their homes waiting for medical staff to come to see them and strictly prohibit social contact.
